# subscript(_:)

**Instance Subscript**

Retrieves an element at a position in the column type.

## Declaration

```swift
subscript(position: Int) -> Any? { get }
```

## Parameters

- **position**: A valid index in the column type.

## Retrieving Elements

- **subscript(_:)**: Retrieves a contiguous subrange of the column type’s elements.
